WEBVTT

00:01:58.975 --> 00:02:00.753
or arranging an in-person meeting.

00:02:02.527 --> 00:02:03.867
This is grooming.

00:02:04.589 --> 00:02:07.159
This is happening, and it's on the rise.

00:02:09.727 --> 00:02:12.183
The question is: What are we going to do?

00:02:12.207 --> 00:02:15.037
Because, in the meantime, kids are alone.

00:02:16.724 --> 00:02:18.740
They finish dinner, go to their rooms,

00:02:18.764 --> 00:02:20.054
close the door,

00:02:20.964 --> 00:02:23.387
get on their computer, their cell phones,

00:02:23.411 --> 00:02:25.621
and get into a bar,

00:02:26.704 --> 00:02:27.864
into a club.